parameters:
\F[\V[2]]\FF[\V[4]]\AA[F]The gaze of a large man who came out of the
elevator falls on the chest area.

\F[\V[2]]\FF[\V[4]]\AA[FF]To reprimand that overly impudent gaze, I
glared at the man.
\n<A man wearing a cardigan>Director Udo! We've been waiting for you!

\n<Minato>\F[\V[2]](I can't just throw it away... Seriously,
what should I do with this...)

\n<Male janitor>Ah, sorry! I just waxed the floor and it's
slippery, so please be careful and use
the elevator \C[0]!

\n<\N[5]>\FF[61]\F[\V[2]]\AA[FF]Here, have some Sisomeru tea... Please cheer
up already.

\n<Minato>\F[\V[2]]\FF[61]\AA[F]Don't just naturally make me try out new
products! It's true that I was a little
curious about this though...

\n<\N[5]>\FF[61]\F[\V[2]]\AA[FF]More importantly... What's really going on?
Even though it was just a meeting, you
haven't been able to concentrate at all,
right?

\n<Minato>\F[\V[2]]\FF[61]\AA[F]I'm telling you, it's nothing... Mmm...
Ugh... What is this? It's so sweet...

\F[\V[2]]\FF[61]\AA[F]The man standing in front of me tightens
the bottle cap he's holding in his hand
and screws the main body into the pocket
of his jacket.

\n<\N[5]>\FF[61]\F[\V[2]]\AA[FF].........Since I only have to show up at the company
today, how about going on a light tour
as a distraction? I have a company
car...
\n<Minato>\F[\V[2]]\FF[61]\AA[F]...Not bad.
\n<Minato>\F[\V[2]]\FF[61]\AA[F]Ah... I just had a little thought.
\n<\N[5]>\FF[61]\F[\V[2]]\AA[FF]I didn't think that. Come on, let's go.

\n<Minato>\F[\V[2]]\FF[61]\AA[F]Hey, don't casually push back the shisomeru
tea!

\n<Excited Senior AD>I just greeted Minato-sama from Guns
earlier! They were, like... super sexy
and cool! N-not that I'm looking at them
like that or anything? I totally respect
them as an artist! Oh, by the way, I
actually went to their concert the other
day, you know...

\n<Socially dying junior AD>(G-grrr... I really need to go to the bathroom!!
This person just keeps talking and
talking!!)

\n<Minato>\F[\V[2]](There are also chestnut soda and tartar
juice, among others. It's quite a
challenging lineup.)
\n<Minato>\F[\V[2]](......Just an ordinary fire extinguisher.)

\n<Minato>\F[\V[2]](It's a sign made of transparent glass. It
seems there are several discussion rooms
on this floor, as well as the second and
third studios.)
\n<Minato>\F[\V[2]](Well-maintained potted plants)

\n<A passionate man's voice>\F[\V[2]]From all of the above... I will prove the
usefulness of the creamy red bean juice!
Please consider changing the lineup of
vending machines...
\n<A man's voice that cuts off abruptly>\F[\V[2]]...No, I mean, it's red bean soup, right?
\n<Angry man's voice>\F[\V[2]]What the hell? You...

\n<Minato>\F[\V[2]](It seems like a pointless debate is
heating up...)

\n<Minato>\F[\V[2]](This is the conference room where we were
having a meeting until just now. We
don't need it anymore.)

\n<\N[5]>\FF[61]\F[\V[2]]\AA[FF]I've been thinking about this every year...
Isn't that outfit hot during the summer?

\n<Minato>\F[\V[2]]\FF[61]\AA[F]It's a custom-made outfit for summer, so
it's not as hot as you think.
